8" src=3D"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAA=
BAAEAAAICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"[eq31]" style=3D"background-position:0px -803=
px;"></span>
</p>
<p>
   Its moment generating function is, for any
   <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"96" height=3D"25" src=3D"=
data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"[eq32]" style=3D"background-position:0px -1824px;vertic=
