</p>
<h3 id=3D"hid13" class=3D"subsubsection">Exercise 1</h3>
<p>
   On each day we play a lottery in which the probability of winning is
   <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"24" height=3D"24" src=3D"=
data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$1%$" style=3D"background-position:0px -2400px;vertical=
-align:-5px"></span>.
</p>
<p>
   What is the expected value of the number of days that will elapse before=
 we
   win for the first time?
</p>

<div class=3D"bproof"><span class=3D"bproof">Solution</span></div>
<div id=3D"idns1" class=3D"clps">
<p>Each time we play the lottery, the
   outcome is a Bernoulli random variable (equal to 1 if we win), with para=
meter
